
'''Yolande Mukagasana''' (wavutse ku ya 6 Nzeri 1954) ni umwanditsi wo mu [[Rwanda]] <ref name="unhcr">http://www.unhcr.org/3b7255132a.html</ref> yandika mu [[Igifaransa|gifaransa]] . <ref name="uwa">http://aflit.arts.uwa.edu.au/YMukagasanaEng.html</ref>

Yabaye umuforomo na anesthetiste ukora mubitaro bya [[Kigali]] . <ref name="uwa" /> Yahungiye mu [[Ububiligi|Bubiligi]] mu gihe cya [[Itsembabwoko ry’u Rwanda ry’1994|jenoside yakorewe Abatutsi mu 1994]]; umugabo we, abana be ndetse nabantu benshi yari azi ko bishwe. Mu [[Bubiligi]], impamyabumenyi ye ntiyigeze imenyekana bityo akora mu rugo . Nyuma yaje kurera bamwe mu bishywa be ababyeyi bishwe hamwe n’imfubyi zo mu [[Rwanda]]. 

Mukagasana yasubiye mu [[Rwanda]] ari kumwe n'umufotozi  Alain Kazinierakis. bakora icyegeranyo c''yitwa Les Blessures du silence'', inkuru zabatangabuhamya kuri [[Itsembabwoko ry’u Rwanda ry’1994|jenoside]]. Bashinze kandi Nyamirambo, point d'appui, umuryango ugamije kwiyubaka. Hamwe nitsinda ry'amakinamico Groupov, yanditse ikinamico ''Rwanda 94'' . 

Yanditse ibitabo bibiri bya ''La mort ne veut pas de moi'' (1997) na ''N'aie pas peur de savoir'' (1999). Yasohoye kandi icyegeranyo ''cy'inkuru De Bouche à oreille'' (2003).   ''La mort ne veut pas de moi'' yahinduwe mucyongereza nka ''Not Time to Die'' by Zoe Norridge muri 2019.

Mu 2002, yahawe igihembo cya Golden Dove for Peace Prize yahawe na Archivio Disarmo. <ref>https://books.google.com/books?id=-YDA0AH59ocC&pg=PA4</ref>

